---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="成功案例 - Training">
  <section class="bg-gray-50 py-20 md:py-32">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
          成功案例
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          见证学习者的成长与成就
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        {[1, 2, 3, 4].map(item => (
          <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 p-8">
            <div class="flex items-start mb-4">
              <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gray-200 mr-4"></div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">客户名称 {item}</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">行业类型</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
              通过使用我们的学习平台，该客户在短时间内实现了团队技能的显著提升，员工满意度和工作效率都有了明显改善。
            </p>
            <div class="flex space-x-8 text-sm">
              <div>
                <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-600">85%</div>
                <div class="text-gray-500">技能提升</div>
              </div>
              <div>
                <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-600">90%</div>
                <div class="text-gray-500">满意度</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
